author: costin
msg: Fix 3358: JDK1.1 compat problems due to missing jar: protocol.
Note that the 'compat' jar: handler is added only if none found, and it support the most minimal
functionality - parsing URLs using the default handler, so new URL( "jar:..." ) works.
In future we may expand this to a complete support for jar: handler in JDK1.1.
